name: Advanced ETL Transformation Script
summary: Learn about .ATS files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Advanced ETL Processor supports many different input file formats, including text, XML, MS Excel, and MS Access files. It also supports live connections via ODBC as well as connections to MySQL, MS SQL Server, Oracle, SQLite, and other database types.

description: Script created by Advanced ETL Processor, a data integration and conversion tool; saves rules for data readers, transformers, and writers; transforms data between source and destination formats when run; can be edited visually as a data flow diagram in the software.
